The paper discusses the use of deep learning methods in Android malware detection, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The use of deep learning also involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. The paper also discusses the limitations and future research directions, which are related to software engineering (cs.SE) and network security (cs.NI).
